# Cached Inference Rules

- Generate stable CSV artifacts under `paths.predictions_dir`; the dashboard should not run model inference live.
- Building predictions must include `scene_id`, `building_id`, predicted label, confidence, review flag, class probabilities, polygon, bbox, and crop paths.
- Scene summaries must include severity counts, priority score, mean confidence, and review flag count.
- Priority score is a demo decision-support signal only. Do not describe it as emergency dispatch logic.
- Keep this package separate from Streamlit UI code and model training code.
